data.description: Looking for a home, you have an opportunity of living in Waterway Estates. This beautiful freshly remodeled ranch style home features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and a 2 car garage, city water/sewer and a long driveway on a corner lot with beautiful matured palm trees and trees. The flat roof over the lanai was replaced in 2022, new lanai, the metal roof was upgraded in 2006, a few windows were replaced in 2008 and the A/C unit with ducts, water heater replaced in 2019, electrical panel replaced in 2014, kitchen remodeled with new appliances, both bathrooms been upgraded fully, new flooring, over all fully remodeled home. Beautiful location for commute and evening walks. Minutes away to restaurants, stores, waterway park with playground/tennis courts, and El Rio Golf Course, Easy to show schedule your showing today!
